reviews.text:
Very nice flavor profile.  Very bright.  The vanilla swirl sits nicely in the background (overnight steep).  This should develope nicely with a longer steep.  The strawberry and dragonfruit are very well balanced.  Thanks ID10-T!&#xD;
&#xD;
Update:  amazing after a week steep.  The dragon fruit is still bright and sweet, but the vanilla swirl developed into a great balanced vape.
